### CRUD PRODUCTOS - Ejemplos de Prueba

### 1. CREAR PRODUCTO
POST http://localhost:8081/api/admin/products
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <TOKEN_ADMIN>

{
  "name": "Hamburguesa Clásica",
  "description": "Carne, queso, lechuga, tomate",
  "price": 25000,
  "productCategoryId": 1,
  "active": true
}

### 2. OBTENER TODOS LOS PRODUCTOS (PAGINADO)
GET http://localhost:8081/api/admin/products?page=0&size=10&sort=id,desc
Authorization: Bearer <TOKEN_ADMIN>

### 3. OBTENER PRODUCTOS ACTIVOS (PAGINADO)
GET http://localhost:8081/api/admin/products/active?page=0&size=10
Authorization: Bearer <TOKEN_ADMIN>

### 4. OBTENER PRODUCTO POR ID
GET http://localhost:8081/api/admin/products/1
Authorization: Bearer <TOKEN_ADMIN>

### 5. ACTUALIZAR PRODUCTO
PUT http://localhost:8081/api/admin/products/1?name=Hamburguesa Premium&price=32000&active=true
Authorization: Bearer <TOKEN_ADMIN>

### 6. ACTUALIZAR SOLO NOMBRE
PUT http://localhost:8081/api/admin/products/1?name=Hamburguesa Deluxe
Authorization: Bearer <TOKEN_ADMIN>

### 7. DESACTIVAR PRODUCTO (BORRADO LÓGICO)
DELETE http://localhost:8081/api/admin/products/1
Authorization: Bearer <TOKEN_ADMIN>

### 8. ACTIVAR PRODUCTO
PATCH http://localhost:8081/api/admin/products/1/activate
Authorization: Bearer <TOKEN_ADMIN>

### 9. DESACTIVAR PRODUCTO
PATCH http://localhost:8081/api/admin/products/1/deactivate
Authorization: Bearer <TOKEN_ADMIN>

### 10. CREAR OTRO PRODUCTO (PIZZA)
POST http://localhost:8081/api/admin/products
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <TOKEN_ADMIN>

{
  "name": "Pizza Margherita",
  "description": "Tomate, mozzarella, albahaca",
  "price": 28000,
  "productCategoryId": 2,
  "active": true
}

### 11. CREAR PRODUCTO (BEBIDA)
POST http://localhost:8081/api/admin/products
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <TOKEN_ADMIN>

{
  "name": "Coca Cola 500ml",
  "description": "Bebida gaseosa",
  "price": 5000,
  "productCategoryId": 3,
  "active": true
}

